com.codecool.anarch1986

Class BasicProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.codecool.anarch1986.BasicProperties

  • public class BasicProperties
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a collector of string arrays. It has several methods for returning these arrays, or one of their elements. The application uses these to set the BasicTrait object fields.
